			<hr>			
		
			<p align=left>
			<h3>Definition expanded to multimedia</h3>
			<p align="left">A method of query creation that allows the user to search for multimedia objects based on an example in the form of...			</p>
			
			<ul>
				<li>
				<p align="left">Text description or concept of the multimedia object (tags, annotations, title, filename, etc.)</li>
				<li>
				<p align="left">Symbolic images or drawings (drawing pen, color selection, icons, etc.)</li>
				<li>
				<p align="left">Multimedia objects (actual image file, video file, etc.)</li>
			</ul>
			</p>
